Zava

Zava dodged the shots from Terrorsaur, and than the ones from KitKat, 
but the shots by Drillbit were an entire surprise. All  of them hit 
her around the lower chest. She fell to the ground with mech fluid 
poured out of her chest. She walked for a few steps, trying to get to 
Deemos, but fell down in pain. She used the comm as her last resort.

"Deemos.....This is Zava....I..I'm closer to the Pred cave(cough)... 
Hurt...badly. Please...help me."

She gives up and goes into stasis lock.
______________________________________________________________________
